      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MY PICASSO (1) goes very well this trip starting 12 times for five wins and four minors. Recorded a 0.8 lengths win (30.32) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. Looks suited here and rates on top. BOOKALOO (3) hit the ground running with a slick early sectional but ran over late and missed the frame when a 3.5 lengths fourth (30.70) over 530m at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from six starts. Has ability and is one of the better chances. DAKOTA MILA (5) could manage only third at this track last time but caught the eye when posting a strong 30.58 over 530m at this track the start prior. Expected to feature on best figures. WOODSIDE JOHNNY (7) ran a flying 30.45 win last time. Not to be underestimated.",
